OL,4,CParkinson's incredibly bravely `
OL,5,CMartin Compston
OL,7,FMartin Compston has lauded Sir Billy
OL,8,FConnolly for dealing with Parkinson's
OL,9,F"incredibly bravely".
OL,11,FThe legendary comedian, 83, was
OL,12,Fdiagnosed with the disease in 2013 and
OL,13,Flater announced his retirement in 2018.
OL,15,FCompston, who is co-hosting Hoolie In
OL,16,FThe Hydro on Saturday dedicated to the
OL,17,FBig Yin, said the Scottish comic has
OL,18,Fbattled the disease "with a smile on
OL,19,Fhis face and cracking jokes that only
OL,20,FBilly can".
