OL,7,FThe actor, who was born in Greenock,
OL,8,Fsaid he was "chuffed" to be asked to
OL,9,Fpresent the night of traditional music
OL,10,Fin Glasgow, despite admitting he is
OL,11,F"not a fan" of public speaking.
OL,13,F"But it's a big Christmas ceilidh
OL,14,Fnight out and a salute to the Big
OL,15,FYin," he told the Press Association.
