OL,3,CSir Billy Connolly battling
OL,4,CParkinson's incredibly bravely `
OL,5,CMartin Compston
OL,7,F"I'm glad about all the murals (of Sir
OL,8,FBilly) that have popped up. I think
OL,9,Fsometimes legends can leave us and
OL,10,Fthen it seems after they're gone
OL,11,Fthere's an outpouring of grief and
OL,12,Fthey don't really know.
OL,14,F"I'm glad the last few years it's been
OL,15,Fmade abundantly clear just how much
OL,16,FBilly is loved and cherished.
OL,18,F"So I think having that salute to him,
OL,19,Fit's lovely."
