OL,7,FMurals celebrating Sir Billy have
OL,8,Fpopped up in recent years, usually
OL,9,Fpainted on to the side of traditional
OL,10,FGlasgow tenements.
OL,12,FCompston said Sir Billy is "the best
OL,13,Fat being Scottish", which is why he is
OL,14,F"globally loved".
OL,16,FHe added: "Obviously, Billy's been
OL,17,Fbattling Parkinson's but he's been
OL,18,Fbattling incredibly bravely and again
OL,19,Fhe's done it with a smile on his face
OL,20,Fand cracking jokes that only Billy can.
