OL,7,F"I'm hoping he's with us for a long
OL,8,Ftime to come."
OL,10,FOrganisers of The Hoolie In The Hydro
OL,11,Fsay it will honour Sir Billy's
OL,12,F"immeasurable" contribution to
OL,13,FScottish comedy, music and culture.
OL,15,FThe annual "Hoolie" is considered to
OL,16,Fbe one of the biggest events of the
OL,17,Fyear for Scottish traditional music.
OL,19,FActs performing this year include
OL,20,FElephant Sessions, Trail West, Manran
OL,21,Fand Beluga Lagoon.
