OL,7,FCompston said the night will honour
OL,8,FSir Billy as a musician, but added:
OL,9,F"There's kind of nothing he can't do
OL,10,Fand he's done it all with a humility
OL,11,Fand obviously a humour that you just
OL,12,Fhave to love.
OL,14,F"When I say to anybody what would be
OL,15,Fthe best way to describe what it's
OL,16,Flike being Scottish or being from the
OL,17,Fwest coast of Scotland, you say Billy
OL,18,FConnolly."
